{
  "texts": [
    "We provide more details next.",
    "Summarize from Feedback (Stiennon et al., 2020) is a human-annotated dataset with summary responses rated on a 7-point Likert scale.",
    "We use its axis subset, which contains absolute scores for overall helpfulness, accuracy, coverage, and coherence.",
    "We use the overall score in our experiments, train on their validation set (8.59k data points), and test on their test set (6.31k data points).",
    "HelpSteer2 (Wang et al., 2024c; d) is a dataset of absolute ratings for instruction-response pairs with correctness, coherence, complexity, verbosity, and overall helpfulness scores."
  ]
}